{"tid":84302,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"狗仔耳仔流血代表啲咩？急","createTime":"2017-01-17T12:18:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-17T13:35:24.000Z","uid":76723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9ce283541f2d13ee201caf3251c2f8ca4c95b883","tid":84302,"uid":76723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T12:18:53.000Z","msg":"我隻狗係領養番黎既 大約2個月個時接左番黎<br />\n有日幫佢抹耳仔 用綿花棒 發現有啲黑紅色（類似乾左既血色）有時佢會&quot;unun&quot;聲 好似好痛咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以喱排都買左啲專係洗狗狗耳仔既藥水幫佢清潔 電筒照入去又睇唔清楚係做咩事<br />\n但佢靜係左耳係咁 右耳就好正常好乾淨<br />\n唔知係咪撞過黎 有冇人既寵物試過咁樣？ 洗唔洗帶佢去睇下獸醫check下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n心急人上 thxx"},{"pid":"6d85a117e50dedf5a7abcd95438add3f2c11a9f0","tid":84302,"uid":19159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T12:25:40.000Z","msg":"唔好再問on9野 睇醫生啦！"},{"pid":"931cd2b7cb9dd1b896ffda7b0c0dfc4c396d01f3","tid":84302,"uid":76105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T12:44:20.000Z","msg":"我個樣似獸醫咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"505c0b15d312b302bc5a35bc7d479e386fdd4cbe","tid":84302,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T12:47:34.000Z","msg":"熱氣<br />\n飲夏枯草降火就無事"},{"pid":"83bfbc4fc56df8d97ea2b5febf4390585c4872e2","tid":84302,"uid":21757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T12:48:30.000Z","msg":"要睇獸醫<br />\n順便要求獸醫示範洗耳仔<br />\n<br />\n唔好用棉花棒"},{"pid":"4d203691418e368e00455c28b7cc018d38e36ac4","tid":84302,"uid":75886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T12:49:14.000Z","msg":"poodle?我隻poodle耳仔成日發炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e099aa51b5d63e7976aa735c4640f494e580a715","tid":84302,"uid":76723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T12:52:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>poodle?我隻poodle耳仔成日發炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.p